Run the following commands from the root of the project:  
---------------------------8<--------------------------- 
Open a new terminal:

	1) Let's build the maven project:
	   ./scripts/BUILDME.sh
	   
	2) Now let's run the embedded server:
	   ./scripts/RUNME.sh   
---------------------------8<---------------------------
Open a new terminal:

	3) Finally, let's start a new client:
	   ./scripts/VIEWME.sh   
---------------------------8<---------------------------
The prerequisites are:

	 * JAVA >= 6
 	   http://java.com/en/download/
 	
 	 * MAVEN >= 3.0.4
 	   http://maven.apache.org/download.html
 	   
	 * Google Chrome :p
 	   http://google.com/intl/en/chrome/